  "description": "SHINEPHI provides non-destructive, real-time inspection with sub-nanometer vertical sensitivity to support zero-defect semiconductor and photonics manufacturing. It delivers this via a patented add-on module that transforms existing imaging systems into high-precision measurement tools. The solution integrates with current inspection equipment to provide stable, in-line nano-characterization and feedback for nano-fabrication. SHINEPHI operates as a B2B hardware provider serving semiconductor and photonics manufacturers seeking improved yield and faster production cycles.",
